CustomField.description: Not on any page layout. Used by PartyPaymentController and Case Payment Process to differentiate RCTs and CPs created through the PartyPaymentVFP as opposed to the ICL. Used to determine if a Task should be sent to the Deputy to Recommend CPs to Case Issues and/or Judgments--PartyPaymentVFP creates LPs and JPs, so a Task is not needed.
CustomField.label: Created Via PartyPaymentVFP
